 & = & \frac{\left(n-1\right)^{k-1}}{n^{k}}\\
E\left(x\right) & = & \sum_{i=1}^{n}i\cdot\frac{\left(n-1\right)^{i-1}}{n^{i}}\end{eqnarray*}

